      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·004.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">蒹葭.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蒹葭蒼蒼，白露為霜。所謂伊人，在水一方。溯洄從之，道阻且長。溯游從之，宛在水中央。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The reeds and rushes are deeply green,
And the white dew is turned into hoarfrost.
The man of whom I think
Is somewhere about the water.
I go up the stream in quest of him,
But the way is difficult and long.
I go down the stream in quest of him,
And lo! he is rightjn the midst of the water.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qinfeng-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
