      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·秦風·004.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">蒹葭.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>蒹葭采采，白露未已。所謂伊人，在水之涘。溯洄從之，道阻且右。溯游從之，宛在水中沚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The reeds and rushes are abundant,
And the white dew has not yet ceased.
The man of whom I think
Is on the bank of the river.
I go up the stream in quest of him,
But the way is difficult and turns to the right.
I go down the stream in quest of him,
And lo! he is on the island in the midst of the water.</seg>
      </tuv>
